OL,3,CMore than 6,000 hospitality venues
OL,4,Cclose amid 'seismic' pressures
OL,6,FMore than 6,000 hospitality venues
OL,7,Fshut their doors for good across the
OL,8,FUK in the face of "seismic" pressures
OL,9,Fon the sector, according to new
OL,10,Ffigures.
OL,12,FIndustry leaders urged the Government
OL,13,Fto support pubs, bars and restaurants
OL,14,Fthrough reductions to tax and national
OL,15,Finsurance payments ahead of the
OL,16,FChancellor's spring budget.
