OL,3,CMore than 6,000 hospitality venues
OL,4,Cclose amid 'seismic' pressures
OL,6,FIt came as the latest hospitality
OL,7,Fmarket monitor from CGA by NIQ and
OL,8,FAlixPartners showed that 6,180
OL,9,Flicensed premises had closed between
OL,10,FDecember 2023 and the same month a
OL,11,Fyear earlier.
OL,13,FIt reflected a slight improvement in
OL,14,Fclosures compared with the previous
OL,15,Fyear, when 8,798 venues shut down.
OL,17,FBut it means almost 23,000 venues have
OL,18,Fclosed in total over the past three
OL,19,Fyears after the heavy toll of the
OL,20,Fpandemic, cost-of-living crisis and
OL,21,Finterest rate rises.
