OL,3,CMore than 6,000 hospitality venues
OL,4,Cclose amid 'seismic' pressures
OL,6,FKate Nicholls, chief executive of
OL,7,Findustry group UKHospitality, said the
OL,8,Fsituation was "unsustainable".
OL,10,FShe said: "These stark closure figures
OL,11,Funderline the seismic challenges
OL,12,Ffacing hospitality businesses.
OL,14,F"It is now a case of supporting the
OL,15,Fsector or losing many businesses for
OL,16,Fgood.
OL,18,F"It's clear that endless price rises
OL,19,Fand an ever-growing tax burden has
OL,20,Fleft businesses on the cliff edge, and
OL,21,Fhas deterred investment.
