OL,6,F"Venues have had no choice but to use
OL,7,Ftheir cash reserves to pay bills, keep
OL,8,Fthe lights on and help people remain
OL,9,Fin jobs, instead of investing in and
OL,10,Fgrowing their businesses."
OL,12,FThe trade body has called for three
OL,13,Fmain measures from the Chancellor to
OL,14,Fhelp support the sector.
OL,16,FUK Hospitality called for business
OL,17,Frates, the property tax affecting high
OL,18,Fstreet firms, to see increases capped
OL,19,Fat 3% and avoid a 6.7% rise expected
OL,20,Fin April.
