OL,6,FIt has called for a temporary
OL,7,Freduction in the lower rate of
OL,8,Femployer national insurance
OL,9,Fcontributions to 10% and an increase
OL,10,Fto the threshold at which employers
OL,11,Fstart paying contributions, ahead of a
OL,12,Frise in the minimum wage.
OL,14,FThe group urged Chancellor Jeremy Hunt
OL,15,Fto lower the rate of VAT for
OL,16,Fhospitality, leisure and tourism firms.
