OL,6,FMs Nicholls said: "With the right
OL,7,Faction from Government, this can be a
OL,8,Fshort-term blip and the sector can
OL,9,Ffulfil its potential in driving
OL,10,Feconomic growth, attracting investment
OL,11,Fand creating jobs."
OL,13,FThe latest data also showed a
OL,14,Freduction in the number of new
OL,15,Fhospitality businesses opening their
OL,16,Fdoors, with higher borrowing costs and
OL,17,Fworries about the economy weighing on
OL,18,Fnew openings.
